        "data": "<h2>Description</h2>\n<p>The services update to 2020.7.1 includes updates to Liferay, and Webserver services. The purpose of this release is to add some performance enhancements to the DXP stack </p>\n<h2>DXP Stack 2020.7.1</h2>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 727px; float: left;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 118px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 148px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Previous Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 157px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Current Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 498px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Docker Images</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr style=\"height: 48px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Backup</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 148px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3.2.9</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 157px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3.2.9</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">liferaycloud/backup:3.2.9</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">CI</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 148px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3.1.3</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 157px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3.1.3</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">liferaycloud/jenkins:2.190.1-3.1.3</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 41.2222px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Database</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 148px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 41.2222px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3.2.5</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 157px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 41.2222px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3.2.5</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/database:3.2.5</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Liferay</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3.0.15</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>3.0.16</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.2.10-sp1-fp3-3.0.16</span><strong>*</strong></p>\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:</span>7.1.10-ga1-fp15-3.0.16</span></p>\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:</span>7.0.10-ga1-fp88-3.0.16</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Search</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3.0.5</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">3.0.5</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">li<span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span>feraycloud/elasticsearch:6.8.4-3.0.5</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">li<span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span>feraycloud/elasticsearch:2.4.6-3.0.5</span></span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Webserver</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3.1.4</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>3.1.5</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">l<span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">iferaycloud/nginx:<span>1.16.1-3.1.5</span></span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>* images for 7.2 fp2 and 7.2 fp4 have also been generated for convenience: </strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.2.10-sp1-fp2-3.0.16</li>\n<li>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.2.10-sp1-fp4-3.0.16</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Update Instructions</h2>\n<p>To apply these updates, update the gradle.properties file the project root folder with the new docker image tags. Here is an example of applying update 2020.1.1 for a 7.2 Liferay project:</p>\n<pre>liferay.workspace.lcp.backup.image=liferaycloud/backup:3.2.9<br>liferay.workspace.lcp.database.image=liferaycloud/database:3.2.5<br>liferay.workspace.lcp.search.image=<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">li<span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span>feraycloud/elasticsearch:6.8.4-3.0.5</span></span></span></span><br>liferay.workspace.lcp.liferay.image=<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.2.10-sp1-fp3-3.0.16</span><br>liferay.workspace.lcp.webserver.image=liferaycloud/nginx:1.16.1-3.1.5<br>liferay.workspace.lcp.jenkins.image=liferaycloud/jenkins:2.190.1-3.1.3</pre>\n<p>Once the gradle.properties file contains the updates, commit the changes to your Git repository.</p>\n<pre>git add gradle.properties &amp;&amp; git commit -m \"update dxp cloud stack to 2020.7.1\"</pre>\n<p>After pushing these changes to the remote repository, a build will be created in Liferay Cloud and it is ready to deploy.</p>\n<h2>Change Log</h2>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 871px; float: left;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 118px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 118px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Version</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 111px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Ticket Number</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 652px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Description</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr style=\"height: 48px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\" rowspan=\"2\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Liferay</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\" rowspan=\"2\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">3.0.16</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">LCP-4571</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 652px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Change protocol used for tomcat connector in server.xml</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">LCP-4020</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 652px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Change parameters of Tomcat Connector to increase max connections</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Webserver</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">3.1.5</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span>LCP-4019</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 652px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span>update HAProxy and Nginx config files to expand workers and set max connections</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>"
      },
